{"tid":1478511,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"捉鬼敢死隊！！","createTime":"2019-08-16T14:14:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T15:30:35.000Z","uid":263702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"75b6e40221335b30a8edfda03e6359a92259a7aa","tid":1478511,"uid":263702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:14:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: brown;\">仆你個街 捉得鬼多易上身呀</span><br />\n<br />\n根據今日咁多消息都話有大量&rdquo;黑人&ldquo;落黎<br />\n佢地一定又想放針玩<span style=\"color: blue;\">七月遇上鬼</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下介紹！！捉鬼五大步！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 覺得怪怪地？ 問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n第一下 問問題個陣唔準圍! <br />\n最緊要有知己良伴係夢中相見 <br />\n一個影 一個問 <br />\n問咩？ 你同佢講你係唔係好憎winnie the pool呀？<br />\nHow's your day? 問下最近地鐵站係邊？<br />\n邊到有廁所？邊到有公園?<br />\n問D<span style=\"color: red;\">無理頭但一定要熟香港環境既問題</span>！<br />\n仲要用<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">英文不斷問</span></span><br />\n答唔到 就叫<span style=\"color: green;\">大聲叫</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">即刻轉英文channel cheers<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"> 2.唔好自己圍 記者圍好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n大家一有風吹異動 就叫記者<br />\n好似駕車咁 <span style=\"color: green;\">保持一米距離</span><br />\n你個知啦 大家身水身汗 <span style=\"color: green;\">有d人體臭特別勁</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">而且記者圍係光明正大</span> 包圍到問到佢想死<br />\n我地圍就會比人話禁錮 睇上去記者圍好睇幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">3. 唔準綁 唔準打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n我明有好多義士好多兄弟姊妹上山期間俾D 仆街整到傷哂甚至離開左<br />\n但係<span style=\"color: red;\">要贏 又唔可以再輸</span><br />\n你地知唔個付鬼個張圖影到好似耶穌咁<br />\n好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔準再有機會俾人看圖說故事<br />\n伸出友誼之手 推人接受下記者訪問<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">4. 郁手！ 錫春袋啦！</span><br />\n捉鬼個個必定係男！一定cool頸！<br />\n我地將預言變成事實!!!!!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大大力咁錫落去啦</span></span><br />\n仲有我平時鐘意唧人嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係影到相之前 必須鬆手</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">5. 睇證件？！ 零資料！</span><br />\n鬼出得黎就預左會爆 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">上次搵到資料 代表對家今次已經有十手準備<br />\n好似黑警個每日見面會咁 資料係零<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n個個就好似純潔既白紙咁<br />\n<br />\n前線! 知道大家每秘都處於高度緊張狀態<br />\n但係冷靜 用一秒鐘思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔確定 就試下用英文溝通</span></span><br />\n答都答唔到既 心照啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d129b8e2980cd094818e6816bcc7db82c42143","tid":1478511,"uid":263702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:16:11.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee781c92c2e92de2ea4f2d4d5891b9310c326f67","tid":1478511,"uid":103102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:17:08.000Z","msg":"[假架d奶] 守護動物同民賤聯fd底<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1477780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1477780</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"88a784385042568dfb4b82616d972935c3ee0cbe","tid":1478511,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:17:33.000Z","msg":"推, 有用POST"},{"pid":"276101fe7ad62a155d8db860cb7dd6fa39254f4a","tid":1478511,"uid":263702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:17:46.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db02b9eb9001597b333e7ea1152fa6be8122b4ca","tid":1478511,"uid":263702,"like":0,"dislike"